===Noun===
'''XOR'''
#Logic function [[exclusive or|exclusive OR]], true if one and only one of two inputs is true. Expression ''exclusive'' as difference from inclusive [[OR]]. In [[infix notation]], it has values

(0 XOR 0) = 0<br>
(0 XOR 1) = 1<br>
(1 XOR 0) = 1<br>
(1 XOR 1) = 0<br>

